data.text: At the end of the day, family is family. I think they’ll make up, it’s good publicity for their new season, bravo at getting us all to talk about it. But I just find it hard to side w/ Kourt’s supposed desire for a quiet life when she’s been a willing participant for 15yrs #KUWTK

And not for nothing but Kourtney can afford to not work because of the brand that @KimKardashian @khloekardashian @KrisJenner etc. built. Their fame is a unit. Their brand is linked, so Kourtney can disavow her sisters but she’s where she is bc of their continuing hard work.
